@node HINT
@title "LastUser: Hints"
@{b} HINTS@{ub}
   These are few advices to use LastUser at its best.

   *Run the program as the very first log in door.

   *The log file is stored in bbs:logfiles/lastusers.text
    (I thought it would be useful for you to know that ;-) )

@endnode

